data.description: Beautifully maintained townhouse in Roswell with 2 car carport!  New kitchen cabinets and granite countertops throughout.  New, never used kitchen appliances; stove/oven, microwave and dishwasher.  Fresh paint throughout.  Nice storage throughout unit with large walk-in closets with built-ins.  Great for first-time homebuyers or investors.  Easy access to GA400, Hwy. 92 and Roswell Square.  Unit is towards the back of the complex, so super private.  Home is move-in ready!
